Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:42.68,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,what truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.93,0:00:46.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I’ll come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.19,0:00:57.61,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I see that bright light.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.57,0:01:03.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,this is all I have
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:06.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,what did you say？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.62,0:01:08.50,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.12,0:01:13.09,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,why do you say？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:18.59,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,刃を砥ぐ、微睡む
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.59,0:01:21.80,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,survive of vision
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.80,0:01:25.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,詩と快楽は未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:27.56,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:29.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I was lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.85,0:01:33.52,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,survive of vision
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:36.69,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,final white heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:40.36,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,さあ奪い合うよ傷を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.74,0:01:42.24,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I don’t know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.24,0:01:44.28,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I don’t know why.
