Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.67,0:00:35.88,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,一二三
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.38,0:00:40.18,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,不死樹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:42.68,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,何為真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.93,0:00:46.64,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,我將成為真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.19,0:00:57.61,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,我看到那片光亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.57,0:01:03.95,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,這就是我的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:06.41,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.62,0:01:08.50,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.12,0:01:13.09,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,你為什麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:18.59,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,磨刀 小憩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.59,0:01:21.80,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,生存之景
